text: The Urosporidae are a family of parasitic alveolates in the phylum Apicomplexa. ==Taxonomy== There is six genera in this family. ==History== This family was created by Léger in 1892.Léger L (1982) Recherches sur les grégarines. Poitiers: Oudin & cie ==Description== There are 45 recognised species in this family. ==References== Category:Apicomplexa families
title: Urosporidae
